Paper-Cleaner
=============

This repository is an AGGREGATE of independently licensed components bundled
together for a single pre-submission workflow (clean a LaTeX source tree for
arXiv, then verify the bibliography). Each component retains its own upstream
license; nothing in this bundle relicenses them. See LICENSE for the scope of
the top-level glue, and each subdirectory's own LICENSE file for the full text.

The two subprojects do not import each other and are executed as separate
programs, so this is a "mere aggregation" under the GNU AGPL v3.0.

